# Metrics Framework

## North Star Metric
Monthly Active Businesses with Healthy Cashflow  
(Positive net cashflow for 3 consecutive months)

## Input Metrics
- Number of financial transactions ingested
- Weekly active users
- Number of data sources connected

## Output Metrics
- Cashflow forecast accuracy
- Monthly revenue growth
- Customer churn rate

## Product Funnel
1. Activation – Business connects bank + accounting tool
2. Engagement – Weekly dashboard usage
3. Retention – Active for 3+ months
4. Monetization – Upgrade to premium forecasting
